.TH IBCHECKFABRIC 8 "September 12, 2011" "Pragmatic Infiniband Utilities" "Infiniband Diagnostics"

.SH NAME
ibcheckfabric \- Perform complete check of the IB fabric

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ibcheckfabric [-hcsd][-C <CA>][-P <port>][-m <node-name-map>]


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
ibcheckfabric is a wrapper script which performs 2 sweeps of the fabric using
iblinkinfo and ibtrackerrors (ibqueryerrors) as it's underlying tools.

.SH OPTIONS

.PP
.TP
\fB\-h\fR
	print help message
.TP
\fB\-c\fR
	clear IB errors after check
.TP
\fB\-s\fR
	SKIP the IB errors check
.TP
\fB\-d\fR
	DON'T ignore down nodes
.TP
\fB\-m <node-name-map>\fR
	specify a different node name map file
.TP
\fB\-C <CA>\fR
   CA name to use
.TP
\fB\-P <port>\fR
   port to use"

.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
iblinkinfo, ibtrackerrors (ibqueryerrors)


